headline: Blackstone (NYSE:BX) Reportedly In Talks To Acquire TXNM Energy's Utility Business
summary: Blackstone (NYSE:BX) is reportedly in talks to acquire TXNM Energy, making the company the leading bidder after others dropped out, according to recent discussions. This potential acquisition focus appears in line with Blackstone's growth strategy and could add weight to its recent 16.84% share price increase over the last month.
